text: Rolan Stanislavovich Khugayev (; born 30 January 1985) is a former Russian football player. ==Club career== He made his Russian Premier League debut for FC Alania Vladikavkaz on 17 October 2004 in a game against FC Saturn Ramenskoye. ==External links== * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:FC Spartak Vladikavkaz players Category:Russian Premier League players Category:FC Olimpia Volgograd players Category:Association football forwards
